==English==

===Adjective===
'''irksome'''

# [[disagreeable|Disagreeable]] or [[troublesome]] by reason of long [[continuance]] or [[repetition]]; [[bothersome]]; [[annoying]]; [[irritating]]; [[wearisome]]; [[tedious]].
